15. Rad1
15. Kh8 {White's position looks good optically, but it is difficult to come up with a plan. The problematic piece is the knight on b3, which is misplaced.16.Na1looks normal, to try to bring the knight to e3 via c2, but it allows16...Qa5!hitting the a4-pawn and preparing ...b5. If White does not do anything, we can slowly build our position on the kingside.} 
