14. Nab5 {14.Bxc4?!Accepting the gift with a knight on a7 is treacherous for White, and you can see the complete analysis in the corresponding chapter.} 
14. Nxb5
15. Nxb5
15. Rxe4 {Material is equal and we have no problems at all.} 
