15. Be4 {This was Chrisitansen's idea. Once the surprise value is gone, the position is more dangerous for White than for Black.15.Nce5Nxc316.dxc3Rxd117.Bxd1Nxe518.Rxe5Bxf319.Rc5+Kd720.Bxf3e621.Bg5Qxf322.gxf3Bxc5=is equal.15.Ne3Nxc3is a much better version of things for us now that White does not have Bg5.} 
