12. Nxe6
12. fxe6
13. Ne2
13. d5
14. Nxd4 {14.exd5exd515.Nxd4cxd4transposes to the text.} 
14. cxd4
15. exd5
15. exd5
16. Bb3
16. Nh5 {After getting the dark-squared bishop, we won't have any problems even if we lose a pawn.} 
